S5.description:
📚 Hi, everyone! Welcome to the Study Squad!

Hi all, I'm Endrit, 29 years old (in my 16th year, haha, just a joke!), a medical student studying in lovely Italy.
The gadget you can see above my glasses is the Luminette Light Therapy Glasses—it replicates the effect of sunlight to enhance your energy and concentration.

I really think that studying can be made easier and more enjoyable with good company. And so, I'm here for the purpose of connecting, inspiring, and growing with all of you. Let's make studying a positive, rewarding, and perhaps even enjoyable thing.

🕒 Daily Streams
I stream nearly daily, 12+ hours of 60/10 Pomodoro sessions.
Start time: around 11:00–11:30 a.m. (UTC+1).
I will put up an advance notice on YouTube if I am unable to stream.

🌐 Join the Community:
Be a part of our friendly and supportive Discord community:
👉 https://discord.gg/aKVAGV2R46
Don't hesitate to send a friend request—let's connect and support one another!

💡 Credits:
My incredible Discord configuration was designed by my talented buddy Haris.
(For business inquiries, remember—I get a cut 😄)

Let's make the most out of this journey—a Pomodoro at a time!

안녕하세요! 법무사 시험을 준비하는 꾸준맨 부맨입니다.
이전에는 장교(ROTC 출신)로 해병대에 6년간 몸담았고, 전역 후 그간 배워보고 싶었던 영상 편집, 코딩, IT(네트워크, 정보보안 등) 여러가지를 공부 했습니다. 그러던 중 좋은 기회를 만나 쿠팡 자회사인 CFS에 입사. 물류센터에서 근무를 했습니다. 군인시절부터 조직(회사)에 의지 하지 않아도 되는 내 능력으로 내 삶을 살고 싶다는 생각을 자주 했고, 경제적으로 독립한 전문가(장인)가 되고 싶었습니다. 

군대 후배의 추천으로 법무사에 도전하게 되었고, 쿠팡 퇴사 후 2021년 8월 말부터 법무사 1차 공부를 시작해서, 1년 만에 집에서 인강으로 22년 법무사 1차 시험에 합격하였고, 당해 2차 시험은 130명 안에 들지 못했습니다. 23년에 2차 공부를 후회없이 하였지만 불합격했습니다. 새로운 마음으로 재동차 도전중입니다. 같이 힘내요🔥🔥🔥

22년 11월 2차 시험이 끝나고 공부가 잘 되지 않아, 2023년 새해를 맞아 스터디윗미를 해보자는 생각을 했고, 열심히 실행하고 있습니다. 항상 시작이 가장 어려운 것 같습니다. JUST DO IT!!!그래도 해보는게 중요하다고 생각합니다.

S22.description:
Welcome to the 24/7 Study With Me stream! Whether you're here for 30 minutes or 6 hours, this stream is built for serious learners only. No distractions, no gossip — just pure focus. Let’s build discipline together. 💪

🕒 ⏰ Stream Format:
🎬 14–15 hours/day: Pre-recorded study videos (looped sessions)
🎥 9–10 hours/day: Live sessions by the host (face cam + real-time Pomodoro)
📌 Chat stays open always, and Nightbot is always active

👮‍♂️ 🚨 Rules (Must Follow):
       📚 This is a study-only stream – no gossip, memes, or unrelated talk
       🚫 No spamming, emoji floods, or unnecessary command use
       🙅 No asking for subs, promotions, or personal info
       🤐 During pre-recorded hours, no casual chatting allowed
       💬 Minimal and study-related messages only
       ❗ Follow Nightbot instructions – it enforces rules automatically

⚠️ Nightbot Strictness:
Nightbot is active 24/7 and automatically moderates chat.
1st violation: ⚠️ Warning or 5-minute timeout
Repeated violations: ⛔ 10+ minute timeout or ban
No appeals – if you break the rules, the bot takes action immediately

Commands You Can Use Anytime:
1.  !start – Start your study session (timer begins)
2.  !stop – End your session (logs time and awards XP)
3.  !task [subject/topic] – Log your current topic (e.g., !task Physics Ch 3)
4.  !goal [your goal] – Set your study goal
5.  !summary – See your total time, XP, task, goal, etc.
6.  !help – Get a list of available commands
This is not just a stream – it's a space to train your focus, build consistency, and grow with like-minded learners.

✅ Subscribe to never miss a session
🤝 Stay respectful, stay disciplined, and let’s grow together

This 24/7 stream from Studyistic is designed to motivate students anywhere, anytime! The study sessions are broadcast live, this makes it possible to study together at the same time with students from all over the world! You might even meet someone who studies the same as you but is 3000 km away from you. How 🆒 isn't this? Feel free to post a message in the chat and in no time you will have a whole group of study friends with you!😍

📌📌HOW TO USE THIS STREAM?
📖During the study sessions (always 50 minutes), study as hard as you can!🫡 
📢Then in the 10-minute break there is room for relaxation. During the break, there are many students who tell in the chat how their session was, what the plans are for the next session, or just something fun they want to share. Sharing with others in the chat what the plans are for the other sessions can be extra motivating.

【 #Studywithme 】 #司法書士試験　合格率5％の狭き門を目指して #勉強中 　#ライブ配信
　(2025年6月9日　夜の部)

昨日の勉強時間は8時間08分でした。
本日は、昨日受験した模試の結果を報告します。
他人のテストの結果を見たくない方は、この下をご覧にならないよう、注意願います。

〈本日の勉強メニュー〉
・雛型3回転目
・80本ノック3回転目
・過去問（刑法）18
・リアリ記述応用編（商登法Q9）
・テキスト読み2回転目（会社法商業登記法）
を中心にやっていきたいと思います。
ーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーー
・
・
・
・
・
・
試験名：伊藤塾　全国公開模擬試験　第2回
試験時間と問題数：
午前→2時間で35問
午後→3時間で35問＋記述各1問（不登法・商登法 各70満点）
※時間内・時間外とは、制限時間内で解いた分と、タイムオーバーだけど択一全問検討したものになります。

【24目標】実施日：2024年6月9日
時間内：（択一午前）19問正解→あと1肢が正しく切れていれば31問正解
　　　　（択一午後）22問正解→あと1肢が正しく切れていれば30問正解
　　　　（記述）不登法36.5点・商登法0点（白紙回答）
時間外：なし（商登法記述を全く解かずに択一を解いたため）

【25目標】実施日：2025年6月8日
時間内：（択一午前）27問正解→あと1肢が正しく切れていれば34問正解
　　　　（択一午後）25問正解→あと1肢が正しく切れていれば30問正解
　　　　（記述）採点中
時間外：（択一午後）27問正解→あと1肢が正しく切れていれば33問正解
ーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーー
このチャンネルは

S33.description:
📩open me:

Hi!
Welcome to another Study with me
Thanks for joining
_________________________

I hope this study video helps you avoid using social media while you study. You will find a quiet and cosy study room ambience in this video when studying at your home. Hopefully, this would get you motivated more for studying. You might hear the rain, birds, typing sounds and the flipping of pages (and cars too, unfortunately) from time to time, and I hope that helps you know that I'm there studying with you!

🔥Key to success - """"BE CONSISTENT""""🔥

___________________________

What are you studying and where are you joining from? I also wonder what type of videos you like, study at the library or study at home? Your opinions are quite important to me; and, if you let me know what type of videos you like to watch, I would be happy. 
_____________________________

✧･ﾟ at the beginning of the study sessions, make sure to:
- turn off anything you're not going to be using to study
- have your materials ready to go
- have drinks/food ready so you don't have to get up to go get necessities
- have a clear idea of what you want to accomplish during the session (i.e., choose a task from your to-do list)


✧･ﾟ during the breaks:
- stop working as soon as the timer hits, even if you're mid-sentence
- make sure to get up, do some simple stretches
- refill anything that needs to get refilled
- talk to friends/update family

✧･ﾟ at the end of this video:
if you want to continue studying, give yourself a longer break and you can the next session video!

you're set to go! ♡
_____________________________
💡Please adjust the volume for each of the background music that comes out.
The ASMR that comes out with 💡 is the sound of burning wood and Rain.

!hi - when you join in👋

!top - Top Points
!points -  to know your points💯

Chat rules:
- Being nice and respectful is mandatory!
- Spamming, harassment, trolling, bullying, repeating and all capital messages are definitely prohibited!

- Please check YouTube's Community Guidelines
_____________________________

To those who are starting :
In order to study or do anything for long periods of time you need a strong purpose and you must be willing to endure challenges. If I can do this, think about what you can accomplish. If you're starting out, start from low intervals(10-30 minutes) and gradually increase once you feel you're comfortable. If you feel like quitting, visualize your goals and evaluate your purpose. Learn to accept challenges in your life to become uncommon.

⏰25分勉強(赤)

を繰り返しています

4回目の休憩は20分です

🍅この放送では25分間の勉強を1回することを "1コマ勉強する" と数えています🍅

【２】

日本で初めてYouTubeLiveを活用したオンライン自習室(通称：満点ルーム)です！

配信主Mantenが運営するオンライン自習室(満点ルーム)で視聴者さんどうし一緒に勉強しませんか? 

スマホやウェブカメラで机をうつせば、あなたの部屋が世界中の人と一緒に勉強できる自習室になります。

たまにYouTubeにうつります。

満点ルームの運営管理は全て かずちゃむ (Twitter: https://twitter.com/kazchamu_manten ) ちゃんにお任せしております

満点ルームの使い方  https://manten120.notion.site/c31bd3cef255412da64be11334516d8d?pvs=4

【３】

世界初!! YoutubeLiveのチャットで学習の記録をつけられます！

コマンド(!25など)をチャットに書き込むことで学習記録をつけることができます。

満点学習帳 ( https://www.mantenroom.com ) と連携しています。

くわしくは上記リンクと下の 【コマンドの使い方】 にて。

【コマンドの使い方】

!25 など!で始まる単語をコマンドと言います。コマンドをチャットに書き込むとbot(自動返信ロボット🤖)を通じて学習の記録をつけられます。

!make

あなたの学習記録ページを作成します

学習記録ページはサイト満点学習帳 ( https://www.mantenroom.com )  に作成されます。

!home

あなたの学習記録ページのURLを返します

!25

1回25分の勉強回数(コマ数)を記録します

今日のコマ数と過去全期間の累計コマ数を返します

学習記録ページに反映されます

(!25aと!25bも同じ機能のコマンドです

ほかの人とタイミングがかぶると反応しないので、

かぶりやすいこのコマンドだけ3種類用意してます)

!delete

学習記録ページに関するすべてのデータを削除します😭

そのほか満点学習帳と連携するコマンドの一覧は『学習記録ページ → ? → 目標設定(仮) → ページ最下部』にて見れます。

ここまでのコマンドは主にコマルチャンbotが返信してくれます⛄

コマルチャンbotが担当するのは満点学習帳・学習記録・満点ルームに関するコマンドです。

満点ルームに関するコマンドは

!room

満点ルーム(オンライン自習室)でカメラをつけて利用した時間を表示する。満点ルームを利用していない人が使うと『0時間0分』と返信されます。

🤖🤖🤖🤖🤖

ここから下のコマンドはNight botが返信してくれます。Night botが担当するコマンドは満点学習帳・学習記録には記録されませんが、モチベを高めたるために自由に使ってくださいませ💨

!in

勉強開始の宣言

!out

勉強終了の宣言

!break 10

10分間の休憩と10分後に必ず戻ってくる宣言

数字は自由に変えられます

数字の前に半角スペースが必要です

他にもいろいろなコマンドがあるよ✨

他の人が使っているのを見て少しずつ覚えていこう！

(Night botが担当する全コマンドのリストはありません)

🤖🤖🤖🤖🤖

【その他】

★チャット欄では勉強に関する話題を書き込んで、視聴者さんどうし切磋琢磨しましょう。勉強から著しく逸脱する話題はNGです。

(しばらく読むのだけに専念して、どんな書き込みが歓迎されるか、雰囲気がつかめるまで書き込みを控えること)

★視聴者さん同士の呼び名について

呼び捨ては禁止です。削除します。

「～と呼んでいいですか？」「～と呼んでください」等のコメントは禁止です。

★BGMは集中力を高める雨音です。ピアノサウンドもミックスしてあります。

チャットで名前が青くなっている人です。(Botを除く)

不適切発言の削除など、平和なチャットを保つため協力してくださっています

・入室用URLをクリックし、最初のページでお名前を入力すると入室できます。スマホの場合、内カメラが起動するので注意。入室後歯車マークの設定画面で背面カメラに変えられます。

S48.title: 50대 감정평가사 도전기! 12HR-STUDY WITH ME (스터디 윗미)/공무원 시험/수험생/전문직 시험/혼자 공부/캠스터디/Huntington Beach/채팅은 쉬는시간에~ 2025-06-09 12:00
S48.description:
50대에 접어들게 되면서....
감히 감정평가사라는 정말 어려운 시험에 도전하게 되었습니다.
서울대, 연고대 출신 합격생이 가장 많고, 
8천여명중에 150~200여명 안팎의 인원만 합격하는 극악의 난이도의 시험입니다.
50대는 1년에 보통 전국에서 2~3명 내외로 합격하더군요....
그런 똑똑하고 체력좋은 젊은 20대~30대 친구들한테 제가 무모한 싸움을 걸었네요.
몸과 머리가 젊을때 같지않지만, 절실함 하나만을 가지고 시작했습니다!
유튜브 공부법은 약하디 약한 저의 의지를 바로 잡는데 꼭 필요한 장치인것 같습니다.
매일매일 이해하지 못하고 암기하지 못함에서 오는 
'불합격하면 어떡하지??'라는 극악의 불안감이 엄습해오지만...
꼭 이겨내겠습니다!
올해 4월 1차, 내년 7월 2차 시험 합격을 목표로 달려가고 있습니다.
저를 아시던 모르시던 한번씩 들어오셔서
*구독, 좋아요 눌러주시고*
[공부 잘하고 있는지 확인해 주시고] 
[만약 나약한 모습을 보인다면 쓴소리해주세요] 
부탁드립니다!!
마지막으로, 
여기 들어 오시는 모든 분들이 준비하시는 시험에 꼭 합격하시길 기원드립니다.
감사합니다!!

As I entered my 50s...
I dare to take a very difficult exam called a certified public appraiser.
It's an extremely difficult exam that only about 150~200 out of 8,000 passed every year in Korea.
Usually, only two or three people in their 50s pass the test a year...
I started a reckless fight against those smart, energetic young people in their 20s and 30s.
My body and head aren't like when I was young, but I started with only one desperation!
The YouTube study method seems to be a necessary device to strengthen my weak will.
Everyday i'm worried that I might fail the exam, but I'll overcome it!
I am studying hard with the goal of passing the first test in April this year. 
and the second exam (Final) in July next year.
Whether you know me or not, please come in.
*Please press subscribe and like*
And please check if I am studying well.
If I don't study or show a weak mental state, please say something bitter.
Please!
Lastly, I hope this real-time streaming will be of great help to your studies.
Thank you!!

SNSや昼寝で現実逃避して1日が終わるのが嫌で、
「せめて好きなことだけでも一生懸命やってみよう！」と思い、
Study With Meの配信を始めました。

知ったことがきっかけで、最近はオランダ語に夢中です🦭
そのほか、韓国語・中国語・英語も勉強しています🌱

みんなで雑談も楽しみながら、5分でも勉強できればOK！
自分のために集中する時間を、一緒に少しずつ積み重ねていきましょう🌙

최근에는 네덜란드의 물개 보호소(일명 물개 유치원)를 알게 된 후, 네덜란드어에 푹 빠져 있습니다🦭

우리 각자를 위한 집중의 시간을, 함께 차곡차곡 쌓아가요🌙
